CustomField.description: Allows the apex batch size to be adjusted for processing Timesheets to create Pay Transactions. The batch size defines how many Timesheets will be processed per batch. When left blank the batch size of 15 will be used
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Allows the apex batch size to be adjusted for processing Timesheets to create Pay Transactions. The batch size defines how many Timesheets will be processed per batch. When left blank the batch size of 15 will be used
CustomField.label: Process Timesheets Batch Size
